vote.title:
A public hearing to receive comments regarding an application for an amendment to the Existing Land Use Map to allow a duplex use on property zoned Tract III within Planned Development District No. 67, on the east side of Tyree Street, north of Savage Street
Recommendation of Staff:  Approval, subject to a revised Existing Land Use Map
Recommendation of CPC:  Denial
